Package: GeRnika
Type: Package
Title: Simulation, visualization and comparison of tumor evolution data.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Aitor", "Sánchez Ferrera", email="aitor.sanchezf@ehu.eus", role=c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6127-0686"))
Author: Aitor Sánchez Ferrera [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Aitor Sánchez Ferrera <aitor.sanchezf@ehu.eus>
Description: `GeRnika` is an open-source R package that is capable of simulating, visualizing and comparing tumor clonal data by using simple commands. This aims at providing a tool to help researchers to easily simulate tumor data and analyze the results of their approaches for studying the composition and the evolutionary history of tumors.
Encoding: UTF-8
imports: data.tree, DiagrammeR, purrr, ggplot2, reshape2,
         colorspace, dplyr
